Package: dieroller
Type: Package
Title: Allows for the user to simulate tosses of different kinds of dice.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Justin Ng
Maintainer: justinriverng@berkeley.edu
Description: This package allows for the user to simulate tossing dice. The user can create different kinds of dice. This means that the user can pick what the faces are and the probabilities of each face occurring. However, there must be 6 sides and the probabilities must be valid probabilities from 0 to 1 that add up to 1.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true